OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen it will be mainly dry with clear
OL,8,Fperiods, but the odd shower possible
OL,9,Fin the south later. A warm night in
OL,10,Fthe west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FAll parts will have a dry
OL,13,Fday with plenty of sunshine. Becoming
OL,14,Fvery warm, locally hot. Chance of a
OL,15,Fshower along the west coast late
OL,16,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
