OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fon Friday with some showers in the
OL,7,Fmorning, these confined to West
OL,8,FHighland by afternoon. Outbreaks of
OL,9,Frain spreading east on Saturday.
OL,10,FScattered showers Sunday, mainly in
OL,11,Fthe north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
